messages.content: Hello! I'm sorry to hear that you're not feeling great. My name is Alex. Can I ask for your name? I'm here to listen and support you. Can you tell me more about what's been going on?
I'm rahul and I've had a bad day at work
Hi Rahul, I'm sorry to hear you had a bad day at work. Work-related stress can really take a toll on our well-being. What specifically happened that made your day so difficult?
